comments: Following the pick, Valanciunas (MEM) and Bazemore (GSW) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
During the rebound, Green (GSW) extends his arm out to tip the ball and marginal contact occurs to Valanciunas' (MEM) arm following his clean tip.
From all available angles, it appears Brooks (MEM) makes clean ball contact on his steal attempt from Wiggins (GSW).
Poole (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Valanciunas' (MEM) path and absorbs the contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Green (GSW) and cleanly blocks the shot.

Bazemore (GSW) extends his arm out and marginal contact occurs to Morant's (MEM) arm as he brings the ball behind his back. Bazemore then makes clean ball contact to dislodge the ball on his driving shot attempt.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Clarke (MEM).
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Brooks' (MEM) path and absorbs the contact.
During the rebound, Morant (MEM) and Bazemore (GSW) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
During the defensive switch on the pick, Clarke (MEM) and Bazemore (GSW) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) moves laterally toward Morant (MEM) and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
During the rebound, Valanciunas (MEM) and Green (GSW) mutually engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Anderson's (MEM) path and absorbs the contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) legally contests Wiggins' (GSW) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.

Morant's (MEM) teammate Clarke (MEM) makes some contact with his arm and the contact affects his ability to cleanly retrieve the rebound. Bazemore (GSW) and Morant both make clean ball contact as they jostle for the loose ball.
Poole (GSW) makes contact to Brooks' (MEM) body as he starts his dribble and the contact affects his SQBR.
Bazemore (GSW) commits a take foul on Morant (MEM).
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Anderson's (MEM) path and absorbs the contact on the dribble hand-off.
Anderson (MEM) jumps for the rebound and incidental body contact occurs with Wiggins (GSW). As they disengage, their arms get tangled briefly and the contact is marginal.
Lee (GSW) tries to steal the ball as Brooks (MEM) brings it up court and any contact with his arm is deemed marginal.
Poole (GSW) commits a take foul on Brooks (MEM).
